## 📋 License Overview

AI Lodi is a premium, commercial blog platform that requires a paid license for use. Different license tiers provide different rights and restrictions.

### 🎯 Available License Tiers

#### 🚀 **Starter License ($299)**
- ✅ Single website/domain use
- ✅ Commercial use rights
- ✅ Source code access
- ✅ 6 months of updates
- ✅ Email support
- ❌ No reseller rights
- ❌ No white-label rights

#### 💼 **Professional License ($599)**
- ✅ Up to 5 websites/domains
- ✅ Commercial use rights
- ✅ Source code access
- ✅ 1 year of updates
- ✅ Priority support
- ✅ Remove attribution
- ❌ No reseller rights
- ❌ No white-label rights

#### 🏢 **Enterprise License ($1,299)**
- ✅ Unlimited websites/domains
- ✅ Commercial use rights
- ✅ Source code access
- ✅ Lifetime updates
- ✅ Priority support
- ✅ Remove attribution
- ✅ Reseller rights
- ✅ White-label rights

